                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="side-fr">
                            <div class="module clearfix">
                                <div class="w-pic"><img src="<@app.link href="public/skin/default/v5/images/img-wangxiaodong.png"/>" alt=""></div>
                                <div class="w-text">
                                    <div><span class="name">王晓东</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;北京教科院基教研中心小学英语教研员</div>
                                    <div>我们非常关注如何用数据分析教学质量，发现教学过程中问题，一起作业提供了非常好的平台。</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="module clearfix">
                                <div class="w-pic"><img src="<@app.link href="public/skin/default/v5/images/img-hanjiqing.png"/>" alt=""></div>
                                <div class="w-text">
                                    <div><span class="name">韩际清</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;山东省中学数学教研员</div>
