                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="module clearfix">
                                <div class="w-pic"><img src="<@app.link href="public/skin/default/v5/images/img-shaowenwu.png"/>" alt=""></div>
                                <div class="w-text">
                                    <div><span class="name">邵文武</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;北京市海淀区高中数学教研员</div>
                                    <div>一起作业是一款能够真正实现数据跟踪，并且提出科学诊断，以及提供改进措施的智能型产品！</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="module clearfix">
                                <div class="w-pic"><img src="<@app.link href="public/skin/default/v5/images/img-fengxiaolin.png"/>" alt=""></div>
